set.seed(63)
jattsm$dataacak<- runif(nrow(jattsm), 2, 50)

warna<- colorBin(
  palette = "Set1", 
  domain = jattsm$dataacak,
  bins = 5)
  
leaflet(jattsm)%>%
addProviderTiles("Thunderforest.OpenCycleMap")%>%
  setView(lng = 112.76, lat = -7.25, zoom = 6) %>%
  addPolygons(fillColor = ~warna(dataacak), 
              fillOpacity = 0.8,
              weight = 1, 
              color = "black", 
              opacity = 1
              ) %>%

addMarkers(lat = -8.184486, lng = 113.668076, popup = "Kabupaten Jember")
